snippet.title: I am Bread - First Look
snippet.description:
Subscribe for more: http://bit.ly/2dYhf3k

The beautiful story of one slice of bread's epic and emotional journey as it embarks upon a quest to become toasted.

2nd trailer here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0h4hbKw-BL0

Get it on PS4! http://bit.ly/1UdpPWB
